text: Dewi Cross (born 6 December 1999) is a Welsh rugby union player who plays for Ospreys as a winger. Cross made his debut for the Ospreys in 2018 against Gloucester having previously played for the Ospreys academy. == References == == External links == *Ospreys Player Profile Category:Welsh rugby union players Category:Ospreys (rugby union) players Category:Living people Category:1999 births
